{"tid":38295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"病人仍在世　殯葬業者互毆急搶客　","createTime":"2016-12-13T23:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T03:59:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5856420d767f9167c28deb4848f91031776f12","tid":38295,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:25:42.000Z","msg":"中國遼寧大連一間醫院本月3日發生一場鬧劇，兩家殯葬業者的職員因「搶客」發生爭執，雙方繼而互毆混戰。離譜的是，他們爭奪的客人仍然在世，正在醫院接受搶救。警方將參與打鬥的7人處以行政拘留15日。<br />\n<br />\n事發於本月3日上午8時許，大連桂林街派出所接到報案，指轄區一家醫院的急診大廳，有兩批人馬鬥毆。警方到場將兩批人分開，並一併帶回派出所調查。警方調閱監視器，發現這兩批人事發前都在急診大廳外等待，但他們沒有一個是病人的家屬。<br />\n<br />\n調查後發現這兩批人分屬兩間殯葬公司。當日上午7時許，救護車送來一位病危患者，該兩批人聞訊趕至，爭奪該名「未來客人」。他們各不相讓，更在急診大廳大打出手。警方事後到場將一干人等帶返派出所調查。<br />\n<br />\n網友砲轟業者行為荒唐，「良心敗壞！希望你多多支持你自己的生意」、「道德淪喪唯利是圖」。另有人表達感嘆，指「這些人為了錢甚麽事都可以做，中國的公民教育要好好加強」。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9378dbe794e9da7e489892b17f7cc0b7af7585a","tid":38295,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"打撚死對方，咪可以搶埋佢啲生意囉。<br />\n<br />\n仲未計佢地果幾單生意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a738a0ccac8e57337506d46b2990a5951c683c","tid":38295,"uid":44933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5fb74874ffe8204dce3327fe4150626b4b00e7","tid":38295,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i3.hoopchina.com.cn/blogfile/201310/29/138303702026084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fblogfile%2F201310%2F29%2F138303702026084.jpg&h=4e50ba44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd960f4369c906cb6889b03f69e40417bf48c5be","tid":38295,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:52:23.000Z","msg":"賺未來錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fe852314b3a26435008ee861807afb1318e8f1","tid":38295,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:58:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b3e2902533a846329b17f31ff7e6d1ea7952fcc","tid":38295,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7d1f63ba58966b9707eab5af16098afc465513","tid":38295,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3b7feb3dee35ca8846540582c2af7e1cdd190e","tid":38295,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:41:17.000Z","msg":"屌那媽，中國都無公民教育，加強條柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88752a9de1fb944ec605336f52a3cb368872a799","tid":38295,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd8fb26278f679ecaaaa1f182f101c24ba4c0c6","tid":38295,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}